        "text": "Every published share surface — card, SVG, CSV, JSONL, transcript, thread, reproduce.json, notebook, signal.json — collapsed into a single timestamped ZIP with a manifest.json that pairs each file with its SHA-256. The twelfth surface, and the first that composes all the others. Researchers grab one URL instead of chaining 10 curl calls; citation hashes match the standalone routes byte-for-byte.",
        "variant": "body"
      },
      "children": []
